    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory2, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, android.view.Window.Callback

    public class Waiter
extends android.app.Activity
    This is the Waiter class. It is responsible for displaying the Waiter layout which lists all the Orders that the waiter can interact with. The Waiter can add a new order, edit or delete the order,calling the OrderView class. This view is also responsible for displaying the Orders that are ready from the kitchen.
